&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About this role in the team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Design at BVNK is scaling into 2 areas: Customer Value Stream (the surfaces our clients use to send, receive, store, and convert) and Core Platform (the systems that make all of it work). We&#39;re hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Principal Product Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to own design for Core Platform and Fincrime.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the chess end of design at BVNK. The work spans onboarding, treasury, reconciliation, billing, core processing, and financial crime — compliance case management, sanctions and transaction monitoring, internal ops tooling, and the platform primitives every customer-facing product depends on. The users are experts — compliance analysts, ops teams, finance — and the design problems are about taming real complexity, holding several constraints in your head at once, and finding the move that&#39;s both correct and elegant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be one of two Principal Designers, reporting to the Head of Design, and partnering closely with the Directors of Product for Platform and Fincrime on long-range strategy. While we continue to build out the senior bench, you&#39;ll also work day-to-day alongside our senior product managers on the problems in front of us. The pod includes our Lead Designer for the Design System, whose work you&#39;ll help shape strategically.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the area grows, this role has a path into design management.&lt;/p&gt;
