&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own design for Core Platform and Fincrime end-to-end&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set the design direction for Product Platform (onboarding, treasury &amp;amp; reconciliation, billing, core processing) and Fincrime (compliance, monitoring, case management)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with PM and engineering to define problems, explore solution spaces, validate concepts, and ship product improvements that move the metrics that matter for these areas — operational efficiency, false-positive rates, time-to-resolution, onboarding conversion, platform reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay involved through launch and iteration. Handoff is not the finish line.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
